[[!meta title="Epic Plane Evolution (YouTube Playables)"]]

This is a guide for Epic Plane Evolution, specifically the YouTube Playables
version. If you didn't know, YouTube has
[Playables](https://www.youtube.com/playables). They are little games that run
in your browser. They're meant for mobile but you can play them on desktop (and
mobile too) by going to Menu (left side) > Explore >
Show more > Playables. You can access Epic Plane Evolution directly
[here](https://youtube.com/playables/UgkxcT8M5bNG1kGoKdTlFWee_ugvWJhkkT-Y).

