Level 4
-------

Fly a paper airplane. Most EPE- (Epic Plane Evolution) heads consider this the
hardest level. Traditional upgrades don't apply here but still only take 4:

1. Great Paper Airplane
2. Super Paper Airplane
3. Hyper Paper Airplane
4. Mega Paper Airplane

