Level 6
-------

Solar glider. Your wings glow gold when in the sun and you gain a significant
speed boost. Otherwise you're as slow as molasses. Keep airspeed steady in every
case. This will involve trading speed for altitude when you're solar-powered and
pitching down to gain speed when you're in the dark.

